  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the gait spatio-temporal parameters of patients with
      degenerative changes in the knee joint and to relate them with 2 questionares (WOMAC and
      SF-36).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
